Html:
hi, in Windows Store Apps I've made a ListView but the problem is I don't know what's the best way to show the titles for each list items in that list. I have searched online mostly everyone is trying to use Columns and Rows. Can you tell me what's the appropriate method for showing the Title for each items in the list &quot;ID&quot;, &quot;NAME&quot;, &quot;Father Name&quot;, &quot;Caste&quot;,&quot;Address&quot;.<br />
<hr />
&lt;ListView Name=&quot;EmployeeList&quot; ItemsSource=&quot;{Binding}&quot; &gt;<br />
<pre><code>        &lt;ListView.ItemTemplate&gt;
            &lt;DataTemplate&gt;
                &lt;StackPanel Orientation=&quot;Horizontal&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;StackPanel.Resources&gt;
                        &lt;Style TargetType=&quot;TextBlock&quot;&gt;
                            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;TextAlignment&quot; Value=&quot;Left&quot;/&gt;
                            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;FontSize&quot; Value=&quot;20&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;
                        &lt;Setter Property=&quot;FontFamily&quot; Value=&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;
                            &lt;Setter Property=&quot;FontWeight&quot; Value=&quot;Bold&quot;&gt;&lt;/Setter&gt;
                        &lt;/Style&gt;
                    &lt;/StackPanel.Resources&gt;
                    &lt;TextBlock Text=&quot;{ Binding Id }&quot;/&gt;
                    &lt;TextBlock Text=&quot;{ Binding Name }&quot;/&gt;
                    &lt;TextBlock Text=&quot;{ Binding FatherName }&quot;/&gt;
                    &lt;TextBlock Text=&quot;{ Binding Caste }&quot;/&gt;
                    &lt;TextBlock Text=&quot;{ Binding Address }&quot;/&gt;
                &lt;/StackPanel&gt;
            &lt;/DataTemplate&gt;
        &lt;/ListView.ItemTemplate&gt;
    &lt;/ListView&gt;</code></pre>
